are you saying rogues should have higher burst DPS than wizards?<br>
<br>
&quot;So are you saying you would think it balanced if wizards did the same sustained DPS as a rogue AND could outdamage them 2 to 1 when desired?&quot;<br>
<br>
when did i say that and what are you smoking?<br>
<br>
wizard burst DPS is, and should be, &gt; all. sustained rog DPS (provided not insane AC mobs) is, and should be, &gt; all.<br>
<br>
however, when did i mention balancing wizards?<br>
